## StringEncoding.cfStringEncoding property

The numeric identifier of this [StringEncoding](./iconv-corefoundation.stringencoding.md)<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
readonly cfStringEncoding: number;
```

## Remarks

This corresponds to the Core Foundation type [CFStringEncoding](https://developer.apple.com/documentation/corefoundation/cfstringencoding?language=objc)<!-- -->.

Note that this is not a \*unique\* identifier. Core Foundation interprets many different values as Mac OS Roman. The `name` is more likely (though still not guaranteed) to be truly unique.
